  "detailed_description": "<strong>A fireball, spirits and a pyramid. What can happen? Move your racket and beat the spirit in a duel.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.poster.avif?t=1757844333\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.webm?t=1757844333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.mp4?t=1757844333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inspired by the hit of the 70s. </h2><strong>Paug </strong> is a small game inspired by the hit of the 70s. It takes place in Egypt where the spirits of the pharaohs wake up, angry after your intrusion into their tombs. You can play alone or up to 2 players locally. What to face your friends for an evening!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/9e4cda58dd5c965a43904aea001c5d94.avif?t=1757844333\" width=608 height=342 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>A fireball, spirits and a pyramid. What can happen? Move your racket and beat the spirit in a duel.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.poster.avif?t=1757844333\" width=610 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.webm?t=1757844333\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/2fac6033b635126f6df0262005ebb6f7.mp4?t=1757844333\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inspired by the hit of the 70s. </h2><strong>Paug </strong> is a small game inspired by the hit of the 70s. It takes place in Egypt where the spirits of the pharaohs wake up, angry after your intrusion into their tombs. You can play alone or up to 2 players locally. What to face your friends for an evening!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1234290/extras/9e4cda58dd5c965a43904aea001c5d94.avif?t=1757844333\" width=608 height=342 /></span>",
